------------------------------------------------------------
- Enter 'List' to print out your saved information
- Enter 'Add' to record a new transaction
- Enter 'Help' to see this message
- Enter 'Exit' to quit the program
- Enter 'Remove' to remove a transaction
- Enter 'Edit' to edit the details of a transaction
- Enter 'Balance' to edit your account information
- Enter 'Erase' to erase your save file
- Enter 'Deposit' to deposit cash to your account
- Enter 'Withdraw' to make money in your account into cash
- Enter 'Clear' to clear the screen
